quran[19]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,52,"Walipoingia kwake na wakasema: Salama! Yeye akasema: Hakika sisi tunawaogopa.",""
  15,53,"Wakasema: Usiogope. Hakika, Sisi tunakubashiria kijana mwenye elimu mno.",""
  15,54,"Akasema: Mnanibashiria nami uzee umenishika! Basi ni kwa njia gani mnanibashiria?",""
  15,55,"Wakasema: Tunakubashiria kwa haki, basi usiwe miongoni mwa wanaokata tamaa.",""
  15,56,"Akasema: Na ni nani anayekata tamaa na rehema ya Mola wake Mlezi isipokuwa wapotovu?",""
  15,57,"Akasema: Hebu mna jambo gani, enyi wajumbe?",""
  15,58,"Wakasema: Hakika sisi tumetumwa kwa kaumu ya wahalifu!",""
  15,59,"Isipokuwa watu wa familia ya Lut'. Bila ya shaka sisi tutawaokoa hao wote.",""
  15,60,"Isipokuwa mkewe. Tumekwishapitisha kwamba huyo hakika atakuwa miongoni mwa watakaosalia nyuma.",""
  15,61,"Basi wajumbe hao walipowajia watu wa familia ya Lut'.",""
  15,62,"(Lut') Alisema: Hakika nyinyi ni kaumu msiojulikana.",""
  15,63,"Wakasema: Bali sisi tumekuletea yale waliyokuwa wakiyafanyia shaka.",""
  15,64,"Na tumekujia kwa Haki, na hakika sisi ni wakweli.",""
  15,65,"Basi ondoka na ahali zako usiku ungalipo, nawe ufuate nyuma yao, wala yeyote kati yenu asigeuke nyuma. Na mwende huko mnakoamrishwa.",""
  15,66,"Na tukamfunulia hukumu hiyo, ya kwamba hata wa mwisho wao hao ikifika asubuhi atakuwa amekwishakatiliwa mbali.",""
  15,67,"Na wakaja watu wa mji huo huku wamefurahi mno.",""
  15,68,"Akasema: Hakika hawa ni wageni wangu. Basi msinifedheheshe.",""
  15,69,"Na mcheni Mwenyezi Mungu, wala msinihizi.",""
  15,70,"Wakasema: Kwani hatukukukataza (kuwakaribisha) walimwengu hawa?",""
